s on the\ndifferent initial sampling methods for the nuclear degrees of freedom is also\ndiscussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Jul 2018 00:29:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Oct 2018 07:04:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 2 Nov 2018 02:24:07 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 11 Mar 2019 07:33:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-12"}
