ological insulator lasers in synthetic\ndimensions and more. Our study here paves the way to these exciting phenomena,\nwhich are extremely hard (if not impossible) to observe in other physical\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Jul 2018 13:21:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-15"}
